lead_paragraph: Paraguay striker Roque Santa Cruz, a veteran of three World Cups, announced on Tuesday he will retire from international football after their qualifiers against Peru and Bolivia.

headline.print_headline: Paraguay's Santa Cruz Announces International Retirement
